milestones.description: Bas Zuiderent has become the top scorer for NED in ODIs with 594 runs, going past Ryan ten Doeschate's 569
This is the lowest match aggregate (419) involving teams Netherlands & Ireland in ODIs
Ireland's 2-run win against Netherlands is the smallest margin of victory in terms of runs in ODIs, beating 74-run win against Bangladesh

stories.title: Ireland squeak home in Stormont thriller
stories.subTitle: Ireland v Netherlands, Quad Series, Stormont
stories.summary: reland revived memories of their nerve-jangling World Cup successes against Pakistan and Zimbabwe, as Kevin O'Brien turned certain defeat into an incredible one-run win by keeping his cool in the final over of the match against Netherlands at Stormont
